</taxonomicName>
sp. (see comment below), and is depicted on page 60. We herewith confirm the depicted specimen as a member of 
<taxonomicName id="4C68EFF1FFCDFFEDFAC0D6FDF2EAF8D0" authorityName="Fischer von Waldheim" authorityYear="1820" box="[1352,1436,685,710]" class="Insecta" family="Pyrochroidae" genus="Pedilus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
